{"tid":1379090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇方法有效啲解決催淚彈","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T02:18:22.000Z","uid":137823,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f4285896897121702991e5ee2a6db78840e3d06f","tid":1379090,"uid":137823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:35:21.000Z","msg":"睇新聞見到其實依家啲人要整熄個催淚彈都要差唔多四五個人行都好近。其實會唔會搵嗰啲膠筒（例如拖地嗰啲筒/屋企啲大size嘅垃圾）直接笠住個催淚彈，一來又唔使咁多人手，二來等啲煙走唔到出嚟，同時又等佢冇氧氣自己熄滅會有效d？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c789906d6ac01390a424034cb3a4f4ed087bb4b4","tid":1379090,"uid":208452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:35:58.000Z","msg":"PUSH<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家入去填低感受</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已經收左集超過二百人嘅感受，幫我地推到上一千、二千 OK ？</span></span><br />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6ba5476e262c371fed771e9e6dcf8f3f4824110c","tid":1379090,"uid":225650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:36:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"050c6927395fe24bde9476a636a5b93b86e25130","tid":1379090,"uid":279145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:38:34.000Z","msg":"個人9狗想法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n密實保鮮袋， 拉埋有三隻色嗰隻，話水都唔會漏水！！ <br />\n<br />\n再用針開個小洞，掉返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無時間就唔開小洞！！ <br />\n<br />\n又方便補充！"},{"pid":"ec379c2cb4766ed3757376c2c9ab0d1f06a65dad","tid":1379090,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:40:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4063aade38cd377cd729b1ff6721906ac14714fa","tid":1379090,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime